na pumps. </P><P>Thanks to Verant for taking the actions to make us better i just hope they dont think these spells are the fix to the necro problem.</P><P>-kryton</P><P>PS: I have a spell idea <BR>Bond of Life:<BR>Cast bond of life on target and when target gets hit necromancer takes the damage. yes this will most likely kill the necro but when the MOB is eating the enchanter cast bond of life on them and start tapping the mob to keep yourself alive.</P><P></P><P></P><P>Do I scare you?<BR>Do you realy want me to scare you?</font></td>
