nk that because we may have been able to solo with ease for a few lvls that now we are forever doomed to being useless in guild raids.</P><P>The important point is that while lvls 1 to 50 can be done in a few months or faster, lvl 60 is forever! Are we forever doomed to uselessness because of a few easy levels? So I ask Abashi, Absor and Verant:</P><P>When do we stop paying???</P><P><BR> Dornette<BR> 56 necromancer<BR> The Nameless</P><P><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
